definitions.definition: A bird of the family Cacatuidae with a curved beak and a zygodactyl foot.
examples: We saw some cockatoos in the aviary.

definitions.definition: A lookout posted during a two-up game, when gambling was illegal.

main_definition: A bird of the family Cacatuidae with a curved beak and a zygodactyl foot. [from 1610s]
secondary_definitions: ( slang , obsolete ) A lookout posted during a two-up game, when gambling was illegal.
